track.name: No Freedom
comments: This song is stunning!  One of her best.
i'm in love with this song ♥
a beautiful recent song by Dido! I love it.
Wasn't that fussed on this as a single, but now I have the album, I think it's awesome!!! :)

I'm thrilled that this lovely song is on Dido's latest album, Girl Who Got Away (Deluxe Edition), which I pre-ordered last night. I can't wait to get it, although I did get the MP3s already, so I could hear all the songs. As good as it gets. If Imogen is my muse, Dido is my Earth Mother. And Anne Marie Almedal is the siren who draws me back again and again, entirely to my delight. So glad I stumbled across last.fm.
Dido has a perfect voice, without peer...so lovely.
It's nice, but not a good choice for 1st single.
I'm amazed by this new song, it's simply great.
